API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>onplaying</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> ミックスインのプロパティで、 <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> のうち <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">playing (en-US)</a></code> イベントを処理するためのものです。</p>\n\n<p><code>playing</code> イベントは、メディアデータが不足して一時停止または遅延した後、再生が開始できる状態になったときに発生します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>element</var>.onplaying = <var>handlerFunction</var>;\nvar <var>handlerFunction</var> = <var>element</var>.onplaying;\n</pre>\n\n<p><code>handlerFunction</code> は <code>null</code> またはイベントのハンドラーを指定する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions\">JavaScript 関数</a>です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#handler-onplaying\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">onplaying の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onplaying","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\" title=\"playing\"><code>playing</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Events/Event_handlers\">DOM イベントハンドラー</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"onplaying は GlobalEventHandlers ミックスインのプロパティで、 event handler のうち playing (en-US) イベントを処理するためのものです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onplaying","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onplaying","local